[package]
authors = [ "Bilal Elmoussaoui <bil.elmoussaoui@gmail.com>",]
categories = [ "gui", "os::linux-apis", "api-bindings",]
description = "XDG portals wrapper in Rust using zbus"
edition = "2021"
exclude = [ "interfaces/*.xml", "ashpd-demo/",]
keywords = [ "portal", "flatpak", "xdg", "desktop", "dbus",]
license = "MIT"
name = "ashpd"
repository = "https://github.com/bilelmoussaoui/ashpd"
version = "0.11.0"
rust-version = "1.75"

[features]
async-std = [ "zbus/async-io", "dep:async-fs", "dep:async-net", "futures-util/io",]
default = [ "tokio",]
backend = [ "async-trait",]
gtk4 = [ "gtk4_x11", "gtk4_wayland",]
gtk4_wayland = [ "gdk4wayland", "glib", "dep:gtk4",]
gtk4_x11 = [ "gdk4x11", "glib", "dep:gtk4",]
raw_handle = [ "raw-window-handle",]
tokio = [ "zbus/tokio", "dep:tokio",]
glib = [ "dep:glib",]
wayland = [ "wayland-client", "wayland-protocols", "wayland-backend",]

[dependencies]
enumflags2 = "0.7"
futures-channel = "0.3"
futures-util = "0.3"
serde_repr = "0.1"

[dev-dependencies]
serde_json = "1.0"
pipewire = "0.8.0"

[dependencies.async-fs]
version = "2.1"
optional = true

[dependencies.async-net]
version = "2.0"
optional = true

[dependencies.async-trait]
version = "0.1"
optional = true

[dependencies.gdk4wayland]
package = "gdk4-wayland"
version = "0.10"
optional = true

[dependencies.gdk4x11]
package = "gdk4-x11"
version = "0.10"
optional = true
features = [ "xlib",]

[dependencies.glib]
version = "0.21"
optional = true

[dependencies.gtk4]
version = "0.10"
optional = true

[dependencies.pipewire]
version = "0.8"
optional = true

[dependencies.rand]
version = "0.9"
default-features = false
features = [ "std", "thread_rng",]

[dependencies.raw-window-handle]
version = "0.6"
optional = true

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0"
features = [ "derive",]

[dependencies.tokio]
version = "1.43"
features = [ "fs", "io-util",]
optional = true
default-features = false

[dependencies.tracing]
version = "0.1"
optional = true

[dependencies.url]
version = "2.5"
features = [ "serde",]

[dependencies.wayland-backend]
version = "0.3"
optional = true
features = [ "client_system",]

[dependencies.wayland-client]
version = "0.31"
optional = true

[dependencies.wayland-protocols]
version = "0.32"
optional = true
features = [ "unstable", "client", "staging",]

[dependencies.zbus]
version = "5.0"
default-features = false
features = [ "url",]

[dev-dependencies.reis]
version = "0.4"
features = [ "tokio",]

[dev-dependencies.tokio]
version = "1.41"
features = [ "rt-multi-thread", "macros",]

[package.metadata.docs.rs]
features = [ "backend", "gtk4", "raw_handle",]
rustc-args = [ "--cfg", "docsrs",]
rustdoc-args = [ "--cfg", "docsrs", "--generate-link-to-definition",]
